description: For some of the most sensational Southern food in San Antonio, come on down to Duke’s truck where they’re serving up scrumptious seafood dishes and all your favorite comfort sides. Their menu features Fish and Shrimp tacos which you can enjoy blackened or fried, as well as hushpuppies, onion rings, chips & salsa & queso, and so much more. Whether you’re hungry for lunch or dinner, Duke’s Southern Cuisine is a great go-to for deliciousness.
name: Duke's Southern Cuisine
